description: The Dragon and Nina square off for Playboy TV. SEXCETERA (Playboy cable TV) wanted to do a special on Ultimate Surrender, so over the course of one day we shot three matches. The rest you will see as bonus updates. This update is relevant in that this is the match that sidelined our Welterweight Champion for three months. We wanted to show this match at the same time we're posting Dragons' come back match.
title: Part 1 of this weeks update.
